column5: Does anyone now if they are open for ice fishing this year? I've been trying to get a hold of them for a couple of days with no success. Do they have an email address or phone # only. I have heard good things about this place and am looking to plan a trip up there this winter. Thanks
Dave can be a strange guy.  they are still open, I believe.  keep at 'er.
Thanks for your reply. I left him a message today. Hopefully he will get back to me in the next couple of days.
